servinfo.title: A/C Refrigerant Pressure Sensor and Its Circuit Inspection (Diesel Engine Model)

ptxt.intxrefpoff: A/C Refrigerant Pressure Sensor Removal and Installation

s1.ptxt: Connect manifold gauge set to the charging valves.
Check output voltage for A/C refrigerant pressure sensor (1) between each sensor terminal, and then compare measured voltage with specified voltage in graph.
If it does not show such characteristic as shown in graph, replace refrigerant pressure sensor with new one.
